data.description:
Discover the charm of this three-bedroom, two-bath home situated on a quiet street with no flood zone.  This home features an attached two-stall garage with an additional 28 x 30 heated shop, offering versatility for various needs.  For the chef in the house we have a well designed kitchen featuring a large island and gas stove.  The very spacious master bedroom boasts a walk-in closet.  The unfinished basement holds untapped potential, providing an opportunity for customization.  Step outside to a huge fenced-in backyard with wood deck, perfect for enjoying outdoor activities or containing your fur babies! 
This property is not just a house; it's a canvas for creating lasting memories, don't miss out on the opportunity to make this one yours!
